When you Own A HOME your payment NEVER goes up.. instead, it goes down over time. AND<br>
YOU RECEIVE MAJOR $$$ TAX BENEFITS!<br>
<br>
You also build $$$ EQUITY over time, our past clients have earned $50,000 to $200,000 in<br>
equity in as little as 2 years. . . could you save $200,000 in 2 years while renting?<br>
<br>
Even if your rent is only $1,500 a month that's $90,000 in 5 years..and $180,000 in 10 years..<br>
that money could be going towards paying down your OWN home and into YOUR pocket<br>
instead of your Landlord's pocket.<br>
<br>
If you OWNED for 10 years, you would never have a payment increase, &amp; YOU WOULD HAVE<br>
PAID OFF MORE THAN HALF OF YOUR OWN HOME AND BUILT MAJOR $$$ EQUITY!<br>
